1️⃣ Wifite – One-click WPA Cracking
apt install wifite
wifite

Captures handshake automatically
Supports WPS brute-force & PMKID
Integrates with aircrack-ng, pyrit, etc.

2️⃣ Airgeddon – Evil Twin + PMKID + MITM Suite

git clone https://github.com/v1s1t0r1sh3r3/airgeddon.git
cd airgeddon
bash airgeddon.sh
Menu-driven

Evil Twin + Captive Portal
PMKID / Handshake attack
SSL-strip, DNS spoofing
3️⃣ Fluxion – Evil Twin Phishing Attack

git clone https://github.com/FluxionNetwork/fluxion.git
cd fluxion
sudo ./fluxion.sh

Creates fake AP with same SSID
Phishing login portal for WPA2
Captures credentials in real time

4️⃣ WiFi Pumpkin 3 – Rogue AP Toolkit

git clone https://github.com/P0cL4bs/wifipumpkin3.git
cd wifipumpkin3
sudo python3 setup.py install

Evil Twin + DNS spoof
Fake Captive Portal
GUI & CLI
Integration with MITM tools
